data.description: Well taken care of and updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home.  Primary suite has walk in closet, sitting area, large bathroom with double vanity, patio door to covered back porch. Open living room with vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace. There is a dining area and breakfast nook, large pantry. Kitchen has new butcher block counters, new backsplash. New flooring and paint thru out. Recessed lighting thru out. Both baths have been updated. Asphalt driveway with room for extra parking. The fenced backyard is well landscaped, storage shed, great covered patio, mature landscaping, underground sprinklers and a 2 car attached garage.
